<blockquote><p>Thanks for putting this presentation online! I&#8217;ve been looking forward to the content of it since your first apprehensive tweets about the topic.</p>

<p>I couldn&#8217;t agree more about the needed changes to the design process, the need to realize that browser results can&#8217;t (nor shouldn&#8217;t) be identical, etc. I&#8217;m hoping by seeing this repeated enough that it will actually sink in with designers that agree a change is needed but keep clinging to their old methodologies.</p>

<p>Thanks, Andy!
</p></blockquote>

